290
00:19:55,770 --> 00:19:58,830
- Really?
- She is my daughter-in-law after all.

291
00:19:58,830 --> 00:20:01,890
Sawa, how's your fever? Are you able to eat?

292
00:20:01,890 --> 00:20:07,410
In that case, I'll get going. Sawa, take care.

293
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:42,220
Welcome home.

294
00:20:42,220 --> 00:20:44,200
Kato is here.

295
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:47,420
- I see.
- Seems like someone was here.

296
00:20:47,420 --> 00:20:50,170
- My friends were here.
- Sawa, too?

297
00:20:50,170 --> 00:20:54,720
That's right. She felt sick so I walked her home just now.

298
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:57,230
Listen, Rikako.

299
00:20:57,230 --> 00:20:59,470
You should

300
00:20:59,470 --> 00:21:01,780
