307
00:21:40,660 --> 00:21:45,570
What a gorgeous painting. This is the best painting so far.

308
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:52,300
Hey, Rikako. What do you think about this painting?

309
00:21:53,390 --> 00:21:58,310
- I don't know.
- I'm asking for your opinion.

310
00:21:58,310 --> 00:22:02,590
The colors are vivid, and it looks intense.

311
00:22:02,590 --> 00:22:04,700
It's a strong painting.

312
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:09,800
Do you think...

313
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:12,590
