327
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:04,250
You don't need to worry. I'm not that foolish
to fall in love with someone's wife anyway.

328
00:23:04,250 --> 00:23:09,330
Besides, she was the one who seduced me.
I have no attachments with her.

329
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:15,700
See you.

330
00:23:20,770 --> 00:23:23,350
Take a bite, even if it's a little.

331
00:23:24,300 --> 00:23:26,600
Thank you very much.

332
00:23:29,500 --> 00:23:33,900
Do you know why Shunsuke loves

333
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:35,630
