344
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:20,970
She was his client's office worker.

345
00:24:22,390 --> 00:24:25,330
Did you know her?

346
00:24:25,330 --> 00:24:27,730
Of course. Because I was concerned about that.

347
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:32,160
I followed him,

348
00:24:33,350 --> 00:24:36,710
