349
00:24:38,610 --> 00:24:42,200
He looked so happy.

350
00:24:42,970 --> 00:24:47,330
He had a smile on his face that I'd never seen before.

351
00:24:48,900 --> 00:24:51,280
It made me so upset.

352
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:55,800
I was so upset that I could die from it.

353
00:24:58,000 --> 00:25:04,300
It seems that they broke up after a few years.

354
00:25:05,180 --> 00:25:11,400
But until the day he died, he never showed me that smile.

355
00:25:12,270 --> 00:25:14,260
Shunsuke...

356
00:25:15,020 --> 00:25:18,160
