365
00:25:57,800 --> 00:26:04,500
Because I couldn't do that. Oh, my.... This onion...

366
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:07,900
<i>My mother-in-law's confession shocked me.</i>

367
00:26:08,840 --> 00:26:14,140
<i>Even now, she is hurting from her husband's affair.</i>

368
00:26:15,690 --> 00:26:18,000
<i>My affair, too...</i>

369
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:21,120
