378
00:28:31,860 --> 00:28:32,920
<i>[You have a new message from Sawa Sasamoto]</i>

379
00:28:32,920 --> 00:28:36,320
<i>[We need to talk. Can I call you tomorrow?]</i>

380
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:52,800
