418
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:15,340
Mr. Kitano.

419
00:32:15,340 --> 00:32:18,850
You'd better not boss me around too much.

420
00:32:18,850 --> 00:32:20,000
What's that supposed to mean?

421
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:22,200
You will find out soon.

422
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:36,070
I'm sorry. I think I lost my car keys.

423
00:32:36,070 --> 00:32:38,200
Can you walk there today?

424
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,600
Did you get your cell phone back?

425
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:43,000
No. It's still under repair.

426
00:32:45,450 --> 00:32:49,210
- I'm off.
- Take care.

427
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:55,600
You told Rikako's husband?

428
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:59,000
