436
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:36,960
Keeping her to yourself is not love. Don't you get it?

437
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:40,140
Have you ever thought about her life?

438
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:49,200
<i>Love is blind.</i>

439
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:55,000
<i>It makes you oblivious to everything around you.</i>

440
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:57,510
<i>My words to Tomoya</i>

441
00:33:57,510 --> 00:34:01,170
