442
00:34:10,680 --> 00:34:12,120
Hello?

443
00:34:12,120 --> 00:34:14,840
<i>Are you free to talk now?</i>

444
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:16,200
Yeah.

445
00:34:17,100 --> 00:34:18,200
Something happened?

446
00:34:18,200 --> 00:34:19,500
No.

447
00:34:20,870 --> 00:34:22,400
Well...

448
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:25,880
