455
00:34:44,860 --> 00:34:46,700
<i>Let's meet and talk.</i>

456
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,120
What?

457
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:52,210
Let's meet and talk for now.

458
00:34:54,670 --> 00:34:57,320
Sorry. I can't.

459
00:35:00,860 --> 00:35:02,540
You are selfish.

460
00:35:04,850 --> 00:35:06,650
I'm sorry.

461
00:35:11,790 --> 00:35:17,780
<i> I'm sorry.   I.... did help your husband.</i>

462
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:20,350
<i>I told him</i>

463
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:23,590
<i>everything that happened so far.</i>

464
00:35:23,590 --> 00:35:28,450
<i>- I'm really sorry from the bottom of my heart. But I want you to...
- I got it.</i>

465
00:35:28,450 --> 00:35:32,640
I've accepted your apology. So leave.

466
00:36:03,500 --> 00:36:05,900
Hello.

467
00:36:06,890 --> 00:36:09,210
- Hello.
- Hello.

468
00:36:22,780 --> 00:36:25,000
Sawa!

469
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,700
Sawa.

470
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:51,960
