and whispering sweet nothings to my ears.

482
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,720
But you...

483
00:37:34,720 --> 00:37:37,140
You have an awful personality,

484
00:37:38,090 --> 00:37:40,000
but you don't belong to any type.

485
00:37:43,460 --> 00:37:45,230
