486
00:37:48,210 --> 00:37:51,820
<i>That's if you can give up everything you have.</i>

487
00:38:03,630 --> 00:38:06,180
I'm sorry.

488
00:38:06,180 --> 00:38:08,170
I don't love you enough

489
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:11,130
