493
00:39:14,090 --> 00:39:16,160
Thanks for waiting.

494
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:17,720
It's fine.

495
00:39:26,250 --> 00:39:29,980
I've been thinking long and hard.

496
00:39:31,890 --> 00:39:35,530
We can't commit such a sin anymore.

497
00:39:35,530 --> 00:39:41,300
I feel bad for your wife, too.
I also think that my husband is important to me.

498
00:39:45,290 --> 00:39:47,530
Honestly,

499
00:39:48,710 --> 00:39:51,020
