517
00:41:20,830 --> 00:41:22,600
"Just a little longer..."

518
00:41:23,660 --> 00:41:25,690
"Just a little longer", was what I thought.

519
00:41:29,460 --> 00:41:31,380
I know I'm selfish.

520
00:41:35,740 --> 00:41:38,270
