528
00:42:27,680 --> 00:42:29,780
But please don't call out to me.

529
00:42:34,570 --> 00:42:36,070
I understand.

530
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:40,760
I won't call out to you, no matter what.

531
00:42:44,490 --> 00:42:46,790
