535
00:43:18,610 --> 00:43:22,420
<i>means that it's also hard for it to end, too.</i>

536
00:43:23,900 --> 00:43:29,900
<i>If I open my mouth, I'd want to take back
what I said about bidding farewell. </i>

537
00:43:31,290 --> 00:43:35,480
<i>So we walked on without words.</i>

538
00:43:40,700 --> 00:43:43,200
This is it, then.

539
00:43:43,950 --> 00:43:45,370
Yup.

540
00:43:52,180 --> 00:43:53,960
Goodbye.

541
00:43:55,440 --> 00:43:57,160
Goodbye.

542
00:44:07,800 --> 00:44:10,370
<i>I can't look back.</i>

543
00:44:11,990 --> 00:44:14,420
<i>If I look back,</i>

544
00:44:15,460 --> 00:44:18,050
<i>what awaits me is true hell.</i>

545
00:44:40,260 --> 00:44:45,480
♫ <i>You and I met as strangers</i> ♫

546
00:44:45,480 --> 00:44:50,880
♫ <i>Last night was last night, and tonight is tonight</i> ♫

547
00:44:50,880 --> 00:44:56,310
♫ <i>Ticklish fingers, counting the moles</i> ♫

548
00:44:56,310 --> 00:45:00,810
♫ <i>Counting from one again</i> ♫

549
00:45:00,810 --> 00:45:06,180
♫ <i>That's right, we're igniting each other once more</i> ♫

550
00:45:06,180 --> 00:45:14,200
♫ <i>when we first meet</i> ♫

551
00:45:17,570 --> 00:45:22,860
♫ <i>It's okay if you forget about me</i> ♫

552
00:45:22,860 --> 00:45:27,450
♫ <i>It's okay if you got astray</i> ♫

553
00:45:27,450 --> 00:45:32,800
♫ <i>I will return time and time again</i> ♫

554
00:45:32,800 --> 00:45:39,440
♫ <i>I will show you that I will return</i> ♫

555
00:45:45,890 --> 00:45:48,270
You know that this has to end someday, right?

556
00:45:48,270 --> 00:45:50,370
Aren't you having a hard time too, Rikako?

557
00:45:50,370 --> 00:45:52,700
You want to lock me in for the rest of my life?

558
00:45:52,700 --> 00:45:56,500
Even if she chooses to go back,
I'm sure she is suffering and regretting.

559
00:45:56,500 --> 00:45:59,570
A scandal is a life-and-death problem for a teacher.

560
00:45:59,570 --> 00:46:02,850
I know that she is not a doll.

561
00:46:03,940 --> 00:46:08,160
You... and that girl... I won't forgive you if you have an affair!

562
00:46:08,160 --> 00:46:11,570
You have no choice but to go back to your mundane life.

563
00:46:11,570 --> 00:46:13,000
If you're not strong,

564
00:46:13,000 --> 00:46:15,190
you have no right to have an affair.
